{"tid":752710,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：元朗西關","createTime":"2018-07-23T04:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T00:01:03.000Z","uid":181719,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8316fb03c21fed3717da1d2686286ddcf21deec","tid":752710,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:41:40.000Z","msg":"我知呢間喺元朗已經神檯級嘅，但區外人就未必知亦都好難食到，難得天黑前喺元朗，又係非繁忙時間，專登喺西鐵站行過去食，都要行10幾分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123710_206353a9adf44d0f01d930f6150038e4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123710_206353a9adf44d0f01d930f6150038e4.jpeg&h=84dfdb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌一個春菜陳腎咸豬骨粥先。其實佢嘅粥係有好多餸揀嘅，由呢啲經典款到蕃茄粥、粟米木耳呢啲比較少機會食到嘅都有。咁點解要食經典款呢？因為第一次黎，唔可以唔試招牌貨先嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡直係一試愛上啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粥底夠綿，又夠杰。豬骨大細適中容易食，又足料又夠咸。其實間舖頭係好多醬料嘅，菜甫都好似有兩款，但根本完全唔駛落任何野送粥。有冇野可以彈呢？有嘅，啲陳腎有輕微嘅腥味，但係瑕不掩瑜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123730_208d193f3fd225141916f7f253b81ed4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123730_208d193f3fd225141916f7f253b81ed4.jpeg&h=d4bda5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123730_42306c96049ec2d2e28f4d1c4f6c5515.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123730_42306c96049ec2d2e28f4d1c4f6c5515.jpeg&h=44315afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得黎到，就算飽都要叫多樣野試嘅，本來好想試吓佢好出名嘅「煎」咸肉糭，但見隔離檯碟腸粉好靚，最後嗌咗個窩蛋碎牛腸，都好少見架。腸粉即叫即做，熱辣辣，啲皮薄到透到入面嘅餡料出黎，若隱若現，性感，飽滿。有冇野可以彈呢？有嘅，隻窩蛋唔係好食得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123749_b31b26e7647e18791a61d4e59fa7d4fd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123749_b31b26e7647e18791a61d4e59fa7d4fd.jpeg&h=148de0f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123749_74d69dea8a3e8b48e362ee4b2f53bd3b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123749_74d69dea8a3e8b48e362ee4b2f53bd3b.jpeg&h=7dfcaf69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123749_90c0b44bb6b8156264a4a650a598c419.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123749_90c0b44bb6b8156264a4a650a598c419.jpeg&h=9ea14bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單60蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f41bc3afbc82a1dfb137a38a8c53ab763f37ed4","tid":752710,"uid":73862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"係屋企附近 的確唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e429797755a62493bd3e296e17f8c4e66e28bc5","tid":752710,"uid":65612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5a60253724b80a5ead3c71cd743a90e3f644bb1a","tid":752710,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"未聽過"},{"pid":"e458010b97c893fd331eaeafa74384dcd2b4e77e","tid":752710,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f41bc3afbc82a1dfb137a38a8c53ab763f37ed4","tid":752710,"uid":73862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"係屋企附近 的確唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"好想試佢啲粉仔，但食唔哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77739e6eb9a2a8964c9f861cc25ea